ulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Codeine, Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, More', 'Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Cobimetinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, More', 1767369485);
